Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}クトリガルに侵攻していた和平反対勢力は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:06.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ほぼ鎮圧された
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが　一部の反対派は逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他の勢力との合流を狙っていると考えられる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこで 君の部隊の力を借りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ディートフリート·ブーゲンビリア海軍大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:27.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なぜ陸軍ではなく 海軍の私を
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君も分かっていると思うが今回の和平調印式は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:37.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大陸全土の今後に関わる重要な式だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:42.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不測の事態に対して考え得る手段をすべて用意しておきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}加えて 陸軍の特殊部隊は解散し
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:48.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有事の力不足は否めない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが 幸いにも君の隊は現役だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しかも 今回の作戦に海軍はうってつけときている
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:03.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厄介事は 弟がいないのなら兄に賴めか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:11.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反対勢力が和平交涉を妨害しに来るのは間違いない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヤツらの動きに 何か目星は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:21.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}3日後に和平の象徴として完成した大陸縱断鉄道に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:26.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}使節と民間のドールが乗りディスタリィから ガルダリクに向かうのだが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.99,0:01:28.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これが危ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:31.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二度と争いは起きてはならん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近隣部隊を自由に使ってかまわん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必ず阻止してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和平か
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬢ちゃんの配達先は本当に ディスタリィでいいんだな？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}補給さえあれば 直接ライデンまで送ってやってもいいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大変な目に遭ったばかりなんだしよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まあ 気が変わったら教えてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごい緊張感ね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それだけこの任務が重要ってことだな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私たちが あの特使と一緒にガルダリクに行って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公開和平書簡の取り交わしを行うのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ それが済めば
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やっと戦争の終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}し… 失礼します　C·H郵便社の方ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今後の予定をご案内させていただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在 本艦はひとひとまるまるにライデン港を出発
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ナーハハルよりレントラー川を北上し
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:42.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メヒティッヒから運河を経由して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}翌 ひとふたまるまるにエクストレーメ国ディスタリィに到着の予定です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:50.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そこで待機している特別列車に特使様と乗車していただきます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:55.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}皆様の安全を期して途中までを船での移動とさせていただいております
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴様らの社長は来ていないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争が終わった途端にさっさと退役しやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰よ　 あんた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ブーゲンビリア大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:15.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ブーゲンビリア？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それつてヴァイオレットの少佐の…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その兄だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何の用です
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下がれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はッ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前たちを目的地まで護衛して
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}調印式を成功させるのが俺の任務だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:37.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}民間のドールというのはお前一人か
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットなら今回は来ません
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それは 何よりだな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:54.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}にしても　まだ ドールなんぞをやっているのかあの人間もどきの出来損ないは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと あんた…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かに あいつは出来損ないかもしれねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでも必死にやってる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:05.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつが書いた手紙で救われてる人もいる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットはステキな手紙を書くんです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}スッと 人の心に滑り込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分が素直になれる手紙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}間に合ったか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:44.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}収容所から脱出したガルダリク兵士 1041名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到着いたしました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}遠いところ ご苦労だった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はッ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メルクロフ准将閣下にはインテンスの時のみならず
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}収容所からも救っていただき感謝しております
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}インテンスか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの屈辱は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忘れがたい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なお 陽動作戦は成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}南のふぬけどもは
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我々がクトリガルで全滅したと思っているでしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よろしい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我々は その間に南北の交通を破壊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その混乱に乗じて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再び インテンスを奪還する
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:41.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鉄道だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:45.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これを たどっていけばライデンシャフトリヒまで行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この鉄道で俺たちの国にも食料や資源が入ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}北と南が和平で結ばれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:02.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ もう争わなくてよくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうしたら 俺の仕事も増えて大忙しだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:10.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嬢ちゃんの手紙をまた運ぶこともあるかもしれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お父さん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おかえりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もうすぐ帰ってくるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨日から今日にかけて沿線で火事があったもようです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}場所は分かるか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確認させます
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}動いたか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}グラジデッツァ大鉄橋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:13.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これが完成したから南北の鉄道が通るようになったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}インテンス
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:32.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火事か？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違います
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爆発の跡があります
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:10:00.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准将閣下に伝えろ「無事 潜入に成功した」と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何で動かないの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近くで火事だってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:14.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァンダルさん　
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの列車のそばに降ろしてください
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ムチャ言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同僚が あの中にいますお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}しゃ～ねえ つかまれ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確認されただけで　昨日から七件の火災が起きています
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:38.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべて鉄道周辺　しかも徐々にこちらに近づいてるな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和平反対派ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:45.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　次はこの車両を狙ってくるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:50.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敵の動きを探るために　先行偵察隊を線路沿いに送れ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:53.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました　ただちに準備させます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　あなたどうしてここに
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}カトレアさんはどこに向かわれるのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}え　ガルダリクとの和平調印式に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}近くに爆発の跡がありました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も同行します
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ダメよ　あなたは会社に戻るの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なぜ貴様がここにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:25.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}クトリガルの任務から帰る途中でお見かけいたしましたので
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}クトリガルだと
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}任務の遂行中にガルダリク軍の残党を見ました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かに見たのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話を聞かせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上空から爆発痕と九か所の黒煙を視認しました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:58.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やはり　この鉄道を足止めして直接攻撃する気か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前方の安全が確認できしだい　大至急発進させる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴様もさっさと降りろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そのような状況ならば私も
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大佐　ご命令を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:17.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴様は今も命令が欲しいだけの道具なんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違います　
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は　もう…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:32.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ブーゲンビリア海軍大佐から報告です
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:46.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}反対派と思われる破壊活動が鉄道周辺で発生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.73,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特使の乗った列車を狙っているもよう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何としても守り抜くように伝えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全軍に出動準備　周辺諸国にも連絡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再び戦争にだけはさせるな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}メルクロフ准将　先行部隊から連絡です
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ディスタリィを出た特別列車に平和使節が乗っていて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イシドルが潜入に成功した
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}列車を襲撃して和平を振り出しに戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:26.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出発後ディスタリィ駅で爆発発生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死傷者はなし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やはりか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何とか　今回はきりぬけたが周辺の警戒を厳にしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰も近づけさせるな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこで仕掛けるつもりなのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:44.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}速度が落ちる所　そしてはかいされると復旧が難しい所
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}グランデッツァ大鉄橋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}トンネルは建設に十年かかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:56.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破壊されたら南北縦断鉄道は当分使用不能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:10.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現在乗客は三両目一番と二番のコンパートメントだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一番には若い男性一名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:18.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}二番には初老の男性一名　それが特使だと思われます
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兵士はすべて四両目以降の車両です
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これより作戦を開始する　行け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はッ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だお前らは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敵襲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}四号車後方だ急げ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外せ　ぐずぐずするな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兵力の一挙無力化を狙っていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:14.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今の揺れは…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}特使様をお連れいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お二人はここにいてください
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後方で数人　前方でも物音がしました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}残された兵力はほぼゼロに近い
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:44.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺がこの列車を止める　お前は中の人間を守れ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やはり命令が欲しいだけか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違います
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:54.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違わない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴様は道具だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺が敵を皆殺しにしろと命じたら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}平然と殺すんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.31,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰も殺しません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}武器はいりません
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.45,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}道具じゃないなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だというんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貴様　ライデンシャフトリヒの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:30.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また会ったな　あの時のクトリガルのガキはどうなった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無様に死んだか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前が怒ることないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あいつが死んだところで誰も悲しまない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}助かった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}女？　行け
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}思い出した　私はあれを戦場で見たことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ライデンシャフトリヒの戦闘人形
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なぜこのようなことを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:37.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前たちに踏みにじられたものを　人を取り返すためだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また戦争を始める気ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前の中で戦争は終わっているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心当たりがあるようだな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私もお前も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:54.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暴力の記憶は火傷のように残って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}永遠に終わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}現実では終わっています
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:00.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わったものか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我々は戦争が終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:08.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死者も生者も栄光に迎えられるのを夢見て戦っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だが現実はどうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上層部は今やお前たちの言いなり
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}命を懸けて民を守ろうとした兵士たちは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:20.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}役立たずとののしられ石を投げられる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我々はすべてに裏切られ捨てられた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ならばすべてを破壊して何が悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう誰にも殺したくありません
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:40.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かかれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なものか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おい大丈夫か
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何が起こってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:03.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:21.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何をしている
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:31.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:32.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}このッ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ディートフリート大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分すら守れないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:48.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不殺とはおこがましい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺の弟ギルは　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなやつを守ろうとしたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう誰も殺したくないのです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐の命令は「生きろ」であって　「殺せ」ではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:07.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦わない殺せない戦闘人形などただの足手まといしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だからギルベルトも守れなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前がギルを殺したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だからお前も死んでしまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早く死ね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:29.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少佐はそれでも「生きろ」と　おっしゃったのです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}守りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も守りたかったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:43.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}准将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:50.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イシドル
Comment: 0,0:00:20.57,0:00:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.85,0:00:04.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}曾经进攻过库图力高的反和平势力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:06.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}基本上已被镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但有部分反对派正在逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们应该打算和其他势力汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以我想借你的部队一用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.64,0:00:22.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}迪特福利特·布干维尔海军大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:27.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么不找陆军 却找我们海军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:34.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你应该也明白 这次和平协议签署仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:37.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是关系到整片大陆将来的重要仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.32,0:00:42.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为防止万一 我想尽可能准备周全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}外加陆军的特种部队已经解散了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:48.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无法否认应急军力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:52.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过幸好你的部队还在服役
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且这次作战是为海军量身定做的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.63,0:01:03.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}弟弟不在 麻烦事就找哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.15,0:01:11.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}反对势力一定会来妨碍和平交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:15.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}关于他们的动向 有什么消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:21.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}三天后 在已完工的和平象征 纵贯大陆铁路上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:26.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}将有使节和民间人偶 从迪斯塔利坐到加达里克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.99,0:01:28.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这趟车非常危险
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:31.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不能让战火重燃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.33,0:01:34.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}附近部队可以任意使用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.28,0:01:36.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定要阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}小姑娘你真要送去迪斯塔利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有补给的话 我能直接送你回莱顿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:31.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是刚受过罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是改变主意了就告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:51.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}气氛好紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:56.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可见这个任务有多重要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:02.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们要和那位特使一起去加达里克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:06.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}交换公开和平书简对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:09.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 完成之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}战争才算结束
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打扰了 是C·H邮政公司的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:25.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我来说明之后的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:34.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}本舰现在于十一点整从莱顿港出发
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从那哈尔沿着兰德勒河北上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:42.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从马齐提经运河 计划于次日十二点整
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到达埃克斯忒梅国迪斯塔利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:50.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}同特使大人一起乘坐当地待命的特别列车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:55.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了保障各位的安全 我们将乘船前去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们的社长没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.88,0:05:07.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}战争刚结束就急着退役
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:10.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}布干维尔大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:15.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}布干维尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那不是薇尔莉特的少佐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:21.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是他哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}退下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:31.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的任务是护送你们到目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:34.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}并保证签署仪式成功举行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.32,0:05:37.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「民间人偶」就你一个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特这次不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:46.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那真是再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:54.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}话说回来 那个仿人的废物还在当人偶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她的确挺不中用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但她还是努力在做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:05.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她写的信还拯救过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.63,0:06:11.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特能写出非常棒的信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:14.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她的信能悄然钻进人的心里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让人变得坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:39.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赶上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:44.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从收容所逃出来的1041名加达里克士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现已到达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}远道而来 辛苦你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}梅尔库洛夫准将阁下 不仅在因坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}连在收容所时也出手相救 感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因坦斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那份屈辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}难以忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:15.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}目前佯攻作战已成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}恐怕南方那群没出息的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:20.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}以为我们已经在库图力高全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们趁机破坏南北交通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}趁乱而入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:32.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}重新夺回因坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.07,0:07:41.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看到铁路了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:45.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}沿着这条路走 就能到莱顿沙夫特里希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:49.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}经由这条铁路 食物和资源就能运入我们国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:52.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}南北将被和平连接在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:02.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 已经不用再争斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样我的工作也会变多 要变忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:10.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说不定还会运到小姑娘写的信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:36.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:38.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:41.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就快回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.18,0:08:57.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}昨天起到今天 沿线发生了火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.34,0:08:59.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}地点在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我去确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:04.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开始行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}格兰迪萨大铁桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:13.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为造好了这座桥 才让南北的铁路连通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:23.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因坦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.98,0:09:32.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:37.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}着火了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有爆炸的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:10:00.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}通知准将阁下 已成功潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么还不发车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:09.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听说附近着火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:14.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}范德尔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.35,0:10:17.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让我在那辆列车旁边下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:18.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:22.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我同事在那辆火车上 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没办法 抓紧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:33.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从昨天起 已确认的火灾就有七场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:38.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}全都是铁路沿线 而且逐渐向我们接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是反和平派吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:45.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 下一个目标就是这辆列车
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:50.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}先派侦察队沿铁路侦察敌情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.47,0:10:53.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白 马上开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 你怎么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嘉德丽雅小姐准备去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:04.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要去参加和加达里克的和平签署仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.09,0:11:07.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}附近有爆炸的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.59,0:11:10.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:16.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不行 你要回公司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:17.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:19.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.47,0:11:25.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去库图力高执行任务的返程中看见了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.28,0:11:27.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你说库图力高？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:31.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在执行任务期间 看见了加达里克的残党
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.53,0:11:34.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你确定看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:40.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:41.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从上空观察到有爆炸痕迹 以及九处黑烟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:58.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们果然打算拦截这条铁路直接攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:02.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一旦确认前方安全 立刻出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也赶快下车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然是这种情况 那我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:10.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大佐 请下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:17.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这家伙 到现在还是个只想要命令的道具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.89,0:12:25.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:32.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}滚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:42.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}布干维尔海军大佐报告称
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.85,0:12:46.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}疑似反对派在铁路周边进行破坏活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.73,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}目标是特使乘坐的列车
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:51.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}告诉他一定要想办法守住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}全军准备出动 也联络周边诸国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:58.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}绝不能让战争再次爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:03.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}梅尔库洛夫准将 先行部队发来消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}从迪斯塔利出发的特别列车上坐着和平使节
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伊西多尔已成功潜入
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}袭击列车 重新化和平为战火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.56,0:13:26.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}出发后 迪斯塔利车站发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}无人受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:29.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:33.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}总算躲开这次袭击了 加强周边警备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不准任何人靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们准备在哪里下手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:44.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}列车必须降速 并且破坏后难以修复的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:46.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}格兰迪萨大铁桥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:50.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}隧道耗费十年才建成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:56.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一旦遭到破坏 南北纵贯铁路将暂时瘫痪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:10.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}目前乘客只有在第三节的一号二号包厢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一号里是一名年轻男性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:18.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}二号里是一名中年男性 应该就是特使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}士兵集中在第四节后的车厢内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:22.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:25.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}作战开始 上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:26.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:52.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:14:59.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在四号车厢后方 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快解开 少磨蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想一口气解除警备兵力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:14.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}刚刚的震动是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:17.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:20.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我去把特使大人带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们两位请留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}后方有数人 前方也有动静
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}剩余兵力几近于零
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:44.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我去停下这趟列车 你去保护里面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:50.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你果然只是想要命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:53.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:54.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你就是个道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:16:00.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要我下令杀光敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你会若无其事地下手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.31,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不会杀死任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:08.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不需要武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:14.45,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然你不是道具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那还能是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:25.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你是莱顿沙夫特里希的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:30.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们又见面了 那时的库图里高小鬼怎样了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:32.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}惨死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:38.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你用不着生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那家伙死了也没人会伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}女人？动手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想起来了 我在战场上见过她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:24.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}莱顿沙夫特里希的战斗人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:31.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:37.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了夺回那些被你们践踏的人和东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们还想挑起战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在你心里战争已经结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看来你心里很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:54.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}关于暴力的记忆像烧伤一样残留在心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}永远不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现实中已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.38,0:18:00.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么可能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.13,0:18:02.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们一直梦想在战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:08.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}死者生者都能赢得荣耀 为此战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:10.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然而现实却如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:13.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}上层对你们唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.82,0:18:16.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}曾经拼命保护民众的士兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:20.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}却被人骂废物 遭人唾弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:25.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一切都背叛并抛弃了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:28.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我们破坏一切又有什么不对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:37.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我再也不想杀死任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:40.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这东西很重要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到底出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:03.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.12,0:20:07.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.61,0:20:13.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:21.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:24.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:31.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}准将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.17,0:20:32.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}迪特福利特大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}连自己都保护不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:48.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还想不杀敌人 简直不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的弟弟基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想保护的是这种家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:57.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我再也不想杀死任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:21:01.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}少佐命令我活下去 而不是杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.21,0:21:07.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不战斗 不杀人的战斗人偶只会拖人后腿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以你才没保护好基尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:12.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是你杀死了基尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以你也去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}快去死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:29.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}即便如此 少佐也叫我活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.16,0:21:34.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也曾想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我也曾想要保护他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:43.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}准将
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.97,0:21:50.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伊西多尔
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:21.23,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたの声がみちしるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:42.69,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}一羽の鳥が　鳴いている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:53.75,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない空に　わたしを探して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:59.57,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}優しさで編み続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:05.21,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}ゆりかごで明日へ行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:11.24,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}晴れの日も雨の日にも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:15.93,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あなたを守るために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:26.84,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}かけがえのない宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:37.66,VIOLET_edjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}名前のない花は　静かに眠るよ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:21.23,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}你的声音 指引我向前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:42.69,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}一只小鸟 婉转鸣叫着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.34,0:22:53.75,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在未知的天空中 四处寻找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.16,0:22:59.57,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}在温柔编织出的摇篮里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:05.21,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}向着明天前进
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.35,0:23:11.24,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}不论天晴 不论风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:15.93,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}只为能守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.41,0:23:26.84,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}独一无二的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:37.66,VIOLET_edch,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur7.5}无名之花 静静地沉眠
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:52.06,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}知らない言葉を　覚えてゆくたび
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:58.56,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}おもかげのなか　手を伸ばすの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.83,0:02:05.16,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}だけど一人では　分からない言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.67,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.26,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}さよならは　苦くて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:20.32,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}アイシテルは　遠いにおいがした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:28.41,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}例えようのない　この思いは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:35.73,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}とても怖くて　だけど　とても愛おしくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:41.99,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}わたし　なんで　泣いてるんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:48.72,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}心になんて　答えたらいい？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:55.47,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}言葉はいつでも　語るでもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:03:01.71,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}そこにあるばかり　つのるばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:10.55,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}わたしは　あなたに　会いたくなる
